    "@value": "As with Monochromator, use CIF conventions. Note: 'Stoichiometry is the relationships between the quantities of reactants and products before, during, and following chemical reactions.'(Wikipedia).  Not sure that's the label we want for this property...Recommend renaming 'sample chemical composition'.",
